text: Holly Mae Muller (born 26 August 1997) is an English singer-songwriter and actress with German ancestry. She represented the United Kingdom in the Eurovision Song Contest in 2023 with her song "I Wrote a Song". The song finished in 25th place in the Grand Final. Her debut studio album Sorry I'm Late was be released in September 2023.
